ref name=\"Al Jazeera 19 April reports\" />\n*Malaysia has reported 84 new cases, bringing the total to 5,389. Malaysian health authorities have also reported 95 recoveries, bringing the total to 3,197. Malaysia also reports one new death, bringing the death toll to 89.<ref>{{cite news |last1=Tang |first1=Ashley |title=Covid-19: 84 new cases, 95 recovered, death toll now at 89 |url=https://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2020/04/19/covid-19-84-new-cases-death-toll-now-at-89#cxrecs_s |accessdate=19 April 2020 |work=[[The Star (Malaysia)|The Star]] |date=19 April 2020 |archiveurl=http://web.archive.org/web/20200419111106/https://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2020/04/19/covid-19-84-new-cases-death-toll-now-at-89 |archivedate=19 April 2020}}</ref>\n*Mexico has reported a total of 7,947 cases and 650 deaths.<ref name=\"Al Jazeera 19 April reports\" />\n*New Zealand has reported 9 new cases (4 confirmed and 5 probable), bringing the total to 1,431 (1,098 confirmed and 333 probable). Health authorities have also reported 45 new recoveries, bringing the total to 912. In addition, authorities confirm one death from the coronavirus during a post-morterm, bringing the total death toll to 12.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/diseases-and-conditions/covid-19-novel-coronavirus/covid-19-current-situation/covid-19-current-cases|title=COVID-19 \u2013 current cases|website=Health.govt.nz|date=19 April 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200419012032/https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/diseases-and-conditions/covid-19-novel-coronavirus/covid-19-current-situation/covid-19-current-cases|archive-date=19 April 2020|access-date=19 April 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.stuff.co.nz/national/health/coronavirus/121074675/coronavirus-southland-case-nzs-first-coronavirus-home-death|title=Coronavirus: Southland case NZ's first Covid-19 home death|first1=Blair|last1=Ensor|first2=Sam|last2=Sherwood|work=Stuff|date=19 April 2020|accessdate=19 April 2020|